FBIS3-52156 "drnes001_r_94003" FBIS-NES-94-001 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Jan 1994 India Italian Foreign Minister Arrives 2 Jan BK0301094894 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 0830 GMT 3 Jan 94 BK0301094894 Delhi All India Radio Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] The Italian foreign minister, Professor Beniamino Andreatta, arrived in New Delhi on a three-day visit last night. He visited Rajghat this morning and laid a wreath at the samadhi [mausoleum] of Mahatma Gandhi. Professor Andreatta is to call on the external affairs minister, Mr. Dinesh Singh, and the president, Dr. Shankar Dayal Sharma, today.
